# Admin Panel — Thiên Nam Engine

> Rules for the "Thiên Đạo" control surface: Next.js admin dashboard for world management.

---

## Core Principle: Power with Accountability

The admin panel is where Thiên Đạo (admins) manage the world. Every action they take must be logged, auditable, and reversible where possible. The panel itself is a thin UI over the same API that the bot uses — with additional admin-only endpoints.

---

## Admin Roles

| Role | Level | Capabilities |
|------|-------|-------------|
| **Thiên Đế** | 1 | All powers, assign other admins |
| **Nam Tào** | 2 | All game management, no admin assignment |
| **Bắc Đẩu** | 3 | Player management, events, no economy changes |
| **Thái Thượng** | 4 | Read-only, player support requests |
| **Địa Quan** | 5 | Probationary, ticket management only |

