## Page Structure

### Dashboard (`/dashboard`)

- Active players (24h, 7d, 30d)
- Economy health indicators
- Active events summary
- Recent admin actions
- Server status (bot online/offline)

### Players (`/players`)

- Search by name or Discord ID
- View character details
- Search and sort leaderboards
- Action: mute, ban, teleport

### Characters (`/characters/[id]`)

- Full character stats
- Inventory
- Action history
- Cooldowns
- Action: reset, delete, adjust stats

### Sects (`/sects`)

- Sect list with treasury, member count, rank
- View sect members and ranks
- Action: dissolve, promote, set leader

### Regions (`/regions`)

- Region status (open/closed/maintenance)
- Active encounters
- Boss spawns
- Action: lock region, unlock region

### Items (`/items`)

- Item database browser
- Add/edit items (via seed update)
- View item effects and rarity

### Events (`/events`)

- List active and past events
- Create new event (draft → preview → publish)
- Edit active event
- End event early
- **Rollback event** if needed

### Logs (`/logs`)

- Action log browser (filterable by type, character, date)
- Public log channel feed

### Audit (`/audit`)

- Admin audit log browser
- Filter by admin, action type, date, target
- Export to CSV

### Economy (`/economy`)

- Currency circulation report
- Shop price trends
- Economy adjustment tools (with preview)
- **Approval required for changes > 5%**

