## Event Creation Flow

The most complex admin flow. Must be a multi-step wizard:

```
Step 1: Basic Info
  ├── Name (text)
  ├── Type (select: WORLD_BOSS, SEASON, MINIGAME, LORE)
  ├── Start time (datetime)
  └── End time (datetime)

Step 2: Effects (repeatable)
  ├── Effect type (select: BUFF, DEBUFF, SPAWN, UNLOCK, CLOSE)
  ├── Target (select: PLAYER, SECT, REGION, ALL)
  └── Effect parameters (dynamic based on type)

Step 3: Rewards (repeatable)
  ├── Item or currency
  ├── Amount
  └── Probabilistic? (yes/no)

Step 4: Requirements
  ├── Minimum realm
  ├── Minimum sect
  └── Region requirement

Step 5: Preview
  ├── Full event JSON
  ├── Mock Discord embed preview
  └── Affected player estimate

Step 6: Publish
  ├── Confirm
  └── → Creates WorldEvent in DB
  └── → Schedules BullMQ job for start/end
```

