## Player Management Actions

### Ban/Permanent Ban

```
1. Select player
2. Choose reason (predefined + custom)
3. Add evidence URL
4. Confirm (requires level 2+)
5. → Creates AdminAuditLog
6. → Updates User record
7. → Notifies player via DM if possible
8. → Posts in admin channel
```

### Character Reset

```
1. Select player + character
2. Player must have submitted in-game request
3. Show what will be reset (full list)
4. Confirm with typed character name
5. → Creates AdminAuditLog with full diff
6. → Transaction: reset all stats, remove items/sect/manual
7. → Keep: username, Discord link
```

### Teleport

```
1. Select player
2. Select target region
3. Optional: reason
4. → Creates AdminAuditLog
5. → Updates Character.regionId
```

