## UI/UX Standards

### Theme

- Dark mode default (matches Discord aesthetic)
- Amber/gold accent color (#f59e0b) for primary actions
- Red (#ef4444) for destructive actions
- Consistent spacing: 4px base unit

### Layout

- Sidebar navigation (collapsible)
- Header with admin role badge
- Breadcrumb for nested pages
- Toast notifications for action results

### Tables

- Sortable columns
- Search/filter bar
- Pagination (max 50 rows per page)
- Row click → detail view
- Bulk select for batch operations

### Forms

- Vertical layout with clear labels
- Inline validation
- Loading states on submit
- Success/error toasts
- Form persistence (draft saves)

