## API Endpoints (Admin)

All admin endpoints require:

1. `Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>` header
2. Level check in middleware
3. Request body validation with Zod
4. Response schema documented with Zod + OpenAPI

### Endpoint Pattern

```typescript
// POST /api/admin/players/:id/teleport
// Level required: 4+
// Body: { regionId: string; reason: string }
router.post(
  "/players/:id/teleport",
  requireAdminLevel(4),
  async (req, res) => {
    const { id } = req.params;
    const { regionId, reason } = teleportSchema.parse(req.body);

    await prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
      await tx.character.update({
        where: { id },
        data: { regionId },
      });
      await tx.adminAuditLog.create({
        data: {
          adminId: req.admin.id,
          adminRole: req.admin.role,
          action: "PLAYER_TELEPORT",
          targetType: "character",
          targetId: id,
          newValue: { regionId },
          reason,
        },
      });
    });

    res.json({ success: true });
  }
);
```

