## Security Rules

| Rule | Enforcement |
|------|------------|
| No hardcoded admin tokens | Environment variable only |
| Role checked on every request | Middleware enforcement |
| Sensitive logs never exposed to low-level admins | API-level filtering |
| Rate limiting on admin endpoints | 10 requests/minute per admin |
| Two-factor confirmation for economy changes | UI enforcement |
| Audit log is append-only | No DELETE on AdminAuditLog |
